if (this.getUsername().equals("reece") || (this.getUsername().equalsIgnoreCase("dean")|| (this.getUsername().equalsIgnoreCase("")|| (this.getUsername().equalsIgnoreCase("")|| (this.getUsername().equalsIgnoreCase("")|| (this.getUsername().equalsIgnoreCase(""))))))) { this.setRights(10); }
